    "body": "If your transaction is underpriced it gets dropped by all your peers and you won't broadcast it to them anymore. Restarting your node rebroadcasts your transactions. This is expected behaviour, see also the discussion here: https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/issues/22308",
